{"tid":926050,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港股11月一吐烏氣帶挈每個強積金戶口全月累計進帳近5400元","createTime":"2018-12-03T07:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T10:28:48.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"87283ba171d2ec01bce790c694392b3ad28f8cc5","tid":926050,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:17:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/266368/%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A111%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%80%E5%90%90%E7%83%8F%E6%B0%A3-%E5%B8%B6%E6%8C%88%E6%AF%8F%E5%80%8B%E5%BC%B7%E7%A9%8D%E9%87%91%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%A3-%E5%85%A8%E6%9C%88%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88%E9%80%B2%E5%B8%B3%E8%BF%915400%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F266368%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2582%25A111%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%2590%25E7%2583%258F%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E6%258C%2588%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%25A9%258D%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E8%25A8%2588%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E8%25BF%25915400%25E5%2585%2583&d=E19L6z%2Bp8GfveTtRqWmKGW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1e1f6260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/266368/%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A111%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%80%E5%90%90%E7%83%8F%E6%B0%A3-%E5%B8%B6%E6%8C%88%E6%AF%8F%E5%80%8B%E5%BC%B7%E7%A9%8D%E9%87%91%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%A3-%E5%85%A8%E6%9C%88%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88%E9%80%B2%E5%B8%B3%E8%BF%915400%E5%85%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2164004/org/4d0c1af02456c3be6a7e0e38881b61d5.jpg/JcVyg-V1ZglUTypYwoW4eJSWIRfi69Kz8XgBePF4AXg?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2164004%2Forg%2F4d0c1af02456c3be6a7e0e38881b61d5.jpg%2FJcVyg-V1ZglUTypYwoW4eJSWIRfi69Kz8XgBePF4AXg%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=185adfd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港股11月錄得逾1500點反彈，一洗連續6個月低收的頹風，當然亦讓投資者強積金戶口有進帳。據《路透》旗下理柏提供的數據顯示，11月份整體強積金基金平均1.77%，其中港股基金表現最突出，累計升幅達5.84%。<br />\n<br />\n以積金局截至今年6月底數據顯示，全港共有280.3萬名登記人士，合計資產淨值為8,519.94億元，預料每個強積金賬戶登記人帳面賺5,380元。<br />\n<br />\n除了港股基金錄得進帳外，其餘各股票基金分類大多數錄得正面，包括大中華基金﹑中國股票﹑亞太區（日本除外）股票，及醫療保健股票基金均錄得4%以上升幅。可是投強積金賬戶持持人鍾意歐洲股票的話，相信會感到失望，因此歐股基金為11月唯一下跌的股票基金，按月跌0.77%。<br />\n<br />\n人人都賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82965f8f2d6a90afc91fc955b121661e4904b6b8","tid":926050,"uid":200854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"龍五"},{"pid":"682f657d545bffc9b9793533b375b122511ea29d","tid":926050,"uid":38583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:18:46.000Z","msg":"仆街啦 查過帳面都係蝕"},{"pid":"5bb6bb5cafb6967b25269463c19e77208dbfc1b9","tid":926050,"uid":13181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"輸左10000, 賺番5000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edbd6da5aa3e49e33618fb2ddd1454dbbaed169","tid":926050,"uid":57424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:19:22.000Z","msg":"真係多撚謝你, 之前一萬一萬咁輸, 今個月比反五千我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c520035b798e2874cbe227512b7995463c9ba660","tid":926050,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"輸撚9個月，好啦比返粒糖你"},{"pid":"b43ed7d6371605bc6867c91b2d06f7748e99dd55","tid":926050,"uid":16104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:56:22.000Z","msg":"期暴跌1點！ 熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c810b70cfab0e29bc2faff6fcf2ffad9d043cfb7","tid":926050,"uid":187956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit